const Link = createLucideIcon('Link', [
  ['path', { d: 'M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71', key: '1cjeqo' }],
  ['path', { d: 'M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71', key: '19qd67' }],

export default Link;
